==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: End-all
<hw>End"-all`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Complete
termination.</def> <mark>[R.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>That but this blow⟦br⟧
Might be the be-all and the <qex>end-all</qex> here.</q>
<rj><qau>Shak.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>the primary or only purpose or goal; <as>as, winning
office is the be-all and <ex>end-all</ex> of a politician's
life</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Endamage</ent>⟦br⟧
